<http://example.com/sensor/Sensor2> a sc:Sensor ;
    sc:name "Sensor2" ;
    sc:observes <http://example.com/property/propertyOfResource1> .

# ===== LOGISTIC ROUTES =====

<http://example.com/logisticroute/LR1> a sc:LogisticRoute ;
